Name: Alien Terminal
About the game: Turn on this alien terminal which is connected to Cyclos by STRO. Earn in game currency accessible on your mobile while your computer does the work. This application is intended for fun. This application is connected to Cyclos a core banking software provided by STRO. You require an account with a Cyclos community to use this app.
